<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4747416>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Onthophagus confusus stat. nov. (a, b) Dorsal habitus of male and female. (c, d) Dorsal habitus of the lectotype and original labels (scale bar: 1 mm). (j, k) Lateral and dorsal view of the parameres (scale bar: 0.05 mm). (l, m) Lamella copulatrix and accessory lamellae. (n) Female genitalia (scale bar: 0.02 mm). Onthophagus nabeleki. (e, f) Dorsal habitus of the lectotype and original labels (scale bar: 1 mm). Onthophagus insularis. (g–i) Dorsal habitus of the lectotype and paralectotype, original labels of the name-bearing type (scale bar: 1 mm). (o, p) Lateral and dorsal view of the parameres (scale bar: 0.05 mm). (q, r) Lamella copulatrix and accessory lamellae (scale bar: 0.02 mm)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4747416/files/figure.png" .
